    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"just existing\" isn't enough. everything i cared about was tied to who i was in that world. now i'm just a shell. people dont just look past things like this, they judge, they whisper. i'm just tired of the weight of it all. it feels more logical to just stop fighting it than to pretend i can start over from zero.",
